commit message: Switch to HTTPS for all links to bitcoin.org.
Fix crash if data usage prefs are not available.
Hint when sending coins to own wallet.
Deny adding of own address to sending addresses.
More descriptive title for dialog for editing address labels.
Transactions in blocks are using their own view binding.
Increase value threshold for 'too much balance' warning.
Custom views can invalidate themselves immediately.
Never show fee for received transactions.
Use Space rather than ImageView for stretch dummy.

Fix height of transaction row.
